{"item_id":"481d34a769:0","text":"External Editors（外部编辑器）"}
{"item_id":"481d34a769:1","text":"Text Editor（文本编辑器）"}
{"item_id":"481d34a769:2","text":"设置用于打开 ASCII RIB 文件的默认编辑器。"}
{"item_id":"481d34a769:3","text":"Node Editor（节点编辑器）"}
{"item_id":"481d34a769:4","text":"Enable Solo（启用 Solo）"}
{"item_id":"481d34a769:5","text":"允许在 Node Editor 中 solo（独显）所选节点，方式与在 Hypershade 中选择 solo 按钮相同。"}
{"item_id":"481d34a769:6","text":"Solo Key（Solo 快捷键）"}
{"item_id":"481d34a769:7","text":"选择用于 solo 节点的 \"hotkey\"（热键），默认为反引号键。"}
{"item_id":"481d34a769:8","text":"Channel Box（通道盒）"}
{"item_id":"481d34a769:9","text":"Attributes in Channel box（Channel box 中的属性）"}
{"item_id":"481d34a769:10","text":"切换 channel box 是否显示 RenderMan 控件。"}
{"item_id":"481d34a769:11","text":"Script Editor Widget（Script Editor 控件）"}
{"item_id":"481d34a769:12","text":"Font Size（字体大小）"}
{"item_id":"481d34a769:13","text":"更改显示字体的大小。"}
{"item_id":"481d34a769:14","text":"Font（字体）"}
{"item_id":"481d34a769:15","text":"（Typeface，字体族）"}
{"item_id":"481d34a769:16","text":"更改编辑器中使用的字体。"}
{"item_id":"481d34a769:17","text":"Tab Width（Tab 宽度）"}
{"item_id":"481d34a769:18","text":"按下 Tab 时，在编辑器中移动指定数量的空格。"}
